metadata.name: Shilly Access Pass #1
metadata.description: Shilly Access Passes are the only way into this new kind of Web3 music community. One where the earliest supporters are not just fans, but also collaborators who can co-write music with Shilly’s band, license their NFTs to be part of Shilly’s story and content, and have a say on everything from which songs he drops to what tattoos he rocks to whether he should have a tabloid romance with Courtney Cox.
